        <article class="reveal bg-white rounded-3xl p-7 shadow-soft"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold">精準挑選</h3><p class="mt-3 text-black/65">依據客戶通路、菜單、成本與規格需求，媒合合適產地與部位。</p></article>
