        <div class="reveal glass rounded-3xl p-7"><p class="text-3xl">🇺🇸</p><h3 class="mt-5 text-xl font-bold">USA Beef</h3><p class="mt-2 text-white/60">穩定規格與高接受度品項。</p></div>
